cas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eAl costado puedes ver la franja característica de Puma\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLa parte superior es de malla técnica con ajuste en cordones\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLa suela es de goma, mientras que la sección del talón cuenta con válvula de aire\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1035931-1101V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Adaptate a terrenos difíciles con los nuevos Cell Solar de Puma.Este tenis cuentan con un","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1035931-1101V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Puma Cell Solar Mujer"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_HomeLoMasNuevo_Mujer_Activitie","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345618049746","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001035931-1101","activityIdentifierID":"716121651","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"2349.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Puma Pounce Lite Mujer","productId":"3074457345618052214","description":[{"longDescription":" \u003cdiv class='container-description'\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePounce Lite: Resistencia para cada carrera\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eLos nuevos Punce Lite de Puma están hechos para que disfrutes de cada carrera. Tienen una espuma ultraligera y un