\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAjuste dinámico con malla\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEntresuela inspirada en el logotipo\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1036459-0000V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Confía en tu capacidad, pero, sobre todo, confía en los nuevos Halo Runner de Under Armou","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1036459-0000V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Under Armour Halo Runner Mujer"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_UnderArmour_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345618011314","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001036459-0000","activityIdentifierID":"716121552","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"2999.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Under Armour Pursuit 4 Hombre","productId":"3074457345617961801","description":[{"longDescription":" \u003cdiv class='container-description'\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePursuit 4, los tenis deportivos que necesitas para dejar los kilómetros atrás.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eAgrega más velocidad gracias al empeine con tejido de malla de alto rendimiento, que además, favorece la transpirabilidad en cada paso que des. También cuentan con Charged Cushioning, espuma moldeada por compresión para una mejor respuesta y durabilidad. ¡No dejes pasar está oportunidad y haz tuyos los nuevos tenis Pursuit 4 de Under Armour!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCaracterísticas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eSuela de goma duradera con diseño flexible\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003ePlantilla de espuma que se amolda al pie\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEmpeine de malla con al menos 30% de material reciclado\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1036385-0001V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Pursuit 4, los tenis deportivos que necesitas para dejar los kilómetros atrás.Agrega más ","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1036385-0001V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Under Armour Pursuit 4 Hombre"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_UnderArmour_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345617961801","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001036385-0001","activityIdentifierID":"716121552","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"1699.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Under Armour Phantom 4 Mujer","productId":"3074457345617882221","description":[{"longDescription":" \u003cdiv class='container-description'\u003e\u003ch4\u003eUsa tus mejores conjuntos con los Phantom 4\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eLos nuevos tenis \u003cstrong\u003eUnder Armour Phantom 4\u003c/strong\u003e para mujer te permitirán verte cada vez mejor. Este para se ha elaborado en una estructura suave y elástica. El cuello de punto te ofrece una sensación similar a la de un calcetín para brindarte un ajuste óptimo. La amortiguación UA HOVR+ reduce los impactos y devuelve la energía para impulsarte hacia adelante. La suela de goma te brinda tracción y durabilidad al caminar.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCaracterísticas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eEstilo casual\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAmortiguación HOVR\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSuela de goma\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1034693-0001V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Usa tus mejores conjuntos con los Phantom 4Los nuevos tenis Under Armour Phantom 4 para m","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1034693-0001V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Under Armour Phantom 4 Mujer"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_UnderArmour_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345617882221","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001034693-0001","activityIdentifierID":"716121552","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"2999.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Under Armour Phantom 4 Hombre","productId":"3074457345617753747",