p\u003eLos nuevos\u003cstrong\u003e Lockdown 7 \u003c/strong\u003eson ligeros y ofrecen la resistencia necesaria para cada temporada. La parte superior de malla es transpirable, además cuenta con revestimientos de cuero para una mayor sujeción. La suela de goma solida y duradera con tracción de espiguilla proporciona un movimiento y un control excepcional.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCaracterísticas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eParte superior de malla\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSuela de goma solida\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEntresuela de EVA\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1036225-0105V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Deslizate sobre la duela con los nuevos tenis Under Armour Lockdown 7.Los nuevos Lockdown","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1036225-0105V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Under Armour Lockdown 7 Joven"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_UnderArmour_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345618055799","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001036225-0105","activityIdentifierID":"716121552","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"1499.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Under Armour Assert 10 Niño","productId":"3074457345618055768","description":[{"lo