that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Nike Court Vision Low Hombre","productId":"3074457345617776214","description":[{"longDescription":" Los nuevos tenis \u003cstrong\u003eCourt Vision Low\u003c/strong\u003e para hombre de la marca \u003cstrong\u003eNike\u003c/strong\u003e logran combinar la esencia del básquetbol retro con la elegancia de un tenis casual. Su parte superior combina piel sintética y genuina que ofrece un estilo muy ochentero, mientras que su diseño Swoosh en dorado con toque retro brinda un aspecto muy elegante. Cuenta con una suela vulcanizada que logra mezclar la suela con la mediasuela para un diseño cómodo y duradero.","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1030680-0100V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Los nuevos tenis Court Vision Low para hombre de la marca Nike logran combinar la esencia","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1030680-0100V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Nike Court Vision Low Hombre"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_Nike_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345617776214","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001030680-0100","activityIdentifierID":"716121590","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"1799.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Nike