nis Nike Quest 6 son el aliado perfecto para alcanzar tus metas deportivas.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCaracterísticas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eSuela de goma\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eTecnología Zoom Air\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAjuste por cordones\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1033199-0001V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Lleva tus carreras al siguiente nivel con los nuevos tenis Nike Quest 6 para hombre.\u0026nbsp","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1033199-0001V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Nike Quest 6 Hombre"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_Nike_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345617927743","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001033199-0001","activityIdentifierID":"716121590","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"1999.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Nike Stellar Ride Niño","productId":"3074457345618060742","description":[{"longDescription":" \u003cdiv class='container-description'\u003e\u003ch4\u003eStellar Ride, los tenis perfectos para los niños.\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eNike Stellar Ride, el tenis diseñado para los niños más activos La parte superior es de malla Engineered Mesh transpirable, mientras que la suela cuenta con una gruesa capa de espuma ComfiRide. La sección del tobillo es acolchada y de perfil bajo. La suela exterior es de goma para ofrecer tracción duradera con múltiples patrones para un mayor agarre.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCaracterísticas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eMediasuela de espuma ComfiRide\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEmpeine de malla Engineered Mesh\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eDetalles de diseño reflectante y empeine con cordones\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1035317-0001V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Stellar Ride, los tenis perfectos para los niños.Nike Stellar Ride, el tenis diseñado par","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1035317-0001V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Nike Stellar Ride Niño"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_Nike_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345618060742","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001035317-0001","activityIdentifierID":"716121590","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"1399.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescription"}]},{"baseMarketingSpotActivityName":"Tenis Nike V5 RNR Mujer","productId":"3074457345618012261","description":[{"longDescription":" \u003cdiv class='container-description'\u003e\u003ch4\u003eEnfrenta cada día con confianza y estilo con los V5 RNR.\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eEste par fusionan comodidad y tendencia. Inspirados en la estética Y2K, estos runners destacan por su entresuela de espuma, robusta pero sorprendentemente ligera, que proporciona un soporte óptimo para tus pies sin sacrificar agilidad. El icónico logotipo Swoosh en 3D no solo añade un toque moderno, sino que también refuerza su carácter retro, haciendo de estos tenis una elección ideal para quienes buscan destacar.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCaracterísticas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eParte superior de malla y ajuste en cordones\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSuela de goma con ranuras\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEntresuela de espuma\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","thumbnail":"images/catalog/default/1034483-1011V1.jpg","language":"-5","shortDescription":" Enfrenta cada día con confianza y estilo con los V5 RNR.Este par fusionan comodidad y ten","fullImage":"images/catalog/default/1034483-1011V1.jpg","productName":"Tenis Nike V5 RNR Mujer"}],"activityFormat":"web","ownerID":"7000000000000001001","activityIdentifierName":"DPV2_Nike_Activities","baseMarketingSpotActivityID":"3074457345618012261","baseMarketingSpotDataType":"CatalogEntry","productPartNumber":"001034483-1011","activityIdentifierID":"716121590","contractPrice":[{"minorVersionNumber":"0","contractPrice":"1999.00","origin":"6","name":"AuroraESite - AuroraESite","contractID":"10005","currency":"MXN","ownerID":"-5000","minimumQuantity":"1.0","majorVersionNumber":"1"}],"attributes":[{"stringValue":"ExtendedSitesCatalogAssetStore","name":"rootDirectory"},{"stringValue":"ShoppingArea/CatalogSection/CatalogEntrySubsection/ProductDisplay","name":"displayTemplate"}],"catalogEntryTypeCode":"ProductBean","activityPriority":"0","properties":[{"baseMarketingValue":"Recommend a catalog entry to a customer that satisfies the chosen target conditions.","baseMarketingKey":"mktActivityDescri